 "blurb": "Destruction Warlock is TBC's endgame caster king: Shadow Bolt machine-gunning with the Improved Shadow Bolt debuff feeding every other warlock's damage too. The spec's phase curve is the steepest in the game — mediocre in Karazhan gear, untouchable in Sunwell. This Phase 2 snapshot aggregates 309 top DPS parses from Serpentshrine Cavern and Tempest Keep; the highest-consensus pick is Belt of Blasting at 92% usage.",
 "statPriorityRationale": "Shadow Bolt spam with Improved Shadow Bolt debuff uptime rewards crit unusually well, and by late phases destruction becomes the highest-ceiling caster in the game — the list leans damage-crit over regen because fights end before mana does.",
